Package jetbrains.mps.ide.projectPane

Interface CreateNodeExtension

  • public interface CreateNodeExtension
    Extra code to run along with creation of a new node. This is similar to NodeFactory, and aims to overcome limitation/feature of NodeFactory, which takes a chance to intervene only for concept hierarchy of newly created node, while this extension does not have such limit.
